Class DefaultPropertyOrderingStrategy

    public class DefaultPropertyOrderingStrategy
extends Object
implements PropertyOrderingStrategy
    The default property ordering strategy is to order the triples according to a lexical sort by property label.
    Author:
    Ian Dickinson, Epimorphics (mailto:ian@epimorphics.com)
